# Local ExternalData test inputs are kept out of git (heavy binaries). The portable
# GoogleTest suite uses synthetic images generated in code plus the committed tiny toy
# models, so these real images/models are only needed for the optional ExternalData
# tests and live in an ExternalData object store (referenced by committed .sha512 links),
# not in the repository.
/test/Data/*.mha
/test/Data/*.mhd
/test/Data/*.raw
/test/Data/Tensor.pt
/test/Data/M258_2_Layers.pt
/test/Data/Test.py

# Local planning / audit notes, not part of the module.
/docs/

# Common build / editor artifacts.
/build*/
*~
.DS_Store
__pycache__/
*.pyc
